idi-Pyr\u00e9n\u00e9es shootings]]. As part of a series of three gun attacks in Toulouse and [[Montauban]], an Islamic French citizen who claimed to be a member of [[al-Qaeda]] shot and killed three children and one Rabbi, and seriously injured another student at the Ozar Hatorah Jewish day school.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/24/opinion/loner-loser-killer.html?scp=1&sq=olivier%20roy&st=cse&_r=0 |work=The New York Times | first=Olivier | last=Roy | title=Loner, Loser, Killer | date=March 23, 2012}}</ref> \n|-\n| May 7, 2012\n| [[Adelaide]], Australia\n|\n| No injuries\n|\n| A Year eight student took a revolver on the grounds of [[Modbury High School]], firing shots. Nobody was injured.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.news.com.au/national-news/shot-fired-from-gun-at-school/story-e6frfkx9-1226352678281 |work=The Advertiser | title=Shot fired from gun taken to Modbury High School | date=May 11, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 19, 2012\n| [[Brindisi]], [[Italy]]\n| Giovanni Vantaggiato, 68\n| 1 dead\n| 5 injured\n|[[2012 Brindisi school bombing]]. A three gas cylinder bomb hidden in a large rubbish bin exploded in front of the Morvillo Falcone high school in Brindisi, Italy, killing one 16-year-old female student and injuring five others \u2013 one seriously. The bomber was identified and arrested on June 6.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-18128170|title=School bomb kills girl in Italy|date=19 May 2012|publisher=|via=www.bbc.co.uk}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://bari.repubblica.it/cronaca/2012/05/19/news/attentato_esplosivo_in_una_scuola_quattro_strudenti_feriti_a_brindisi_l_esplosione_nell_istituto_professionale_nei_pressi_-35438304/|title=La cronaca / Bomba a Brindisi, dolore e rabbia Fischi ai politici: \"Ora ammazzateci tutti\" - Bari - Repubblica.it|website=Bari - La Repubblica}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 25, 2012\n| [[Sankt Poelten]], [[Austria]]\n| Unidentified male, 37\n| 1 dead \n| 1 injured\n| Shortly after 8:00 local time, a